layout_dets.latex: \begin{array}{r l}&{\mathbb{E}_{u\sim N(0,1/\lambda_{1})}[f(z;u)]\le\displaystyle\int_{-\log(\rho k)/2}^{\log(\rho k)/2}f(z;u)g(u)\mathrm{d}u+\displaystyle\int_{|u|\ge\log(\rho k)/2}f(z;u)g(u)\mathrm{d}z}\\ &{\qquad\qquad\qquad\le O(1/(\rho k))+O\left(\frac{\exp(-\lambda_{1}\log(\rho k)^{2}/2)}{\log(\rho k)}\right)}\\ &{\qquad\qquad\qquad=O(1/(\rho k)),}\end{array}
